Detailed Description

Class that maintains the all the inline help documentation for DAZ Studio.

Use DzApp::getHelpMgr() to access.

See DAZ Studio Help Generator for information on how to populate the Help Manager.

QString *  group = NULL,
QString *  description = NULL,
QString *  toolTip = NULL,
QString *  statusTip = NULL,
QString *  helpString = NULL 
) const

Gets the strings for a help item if the help item exists.

Parameters:
label The label of the help item to look up.
group If not NULL, this will be set to the group from the help item.
description If not NULL, this will be set to the description from the help item.
toolTip If not NULL, this will be set to the tool tip from the help item.
statusTip If not NULL, this will be set to the status tip from the help item.
helpString If not NULL, this will be set to the whats this help string from the help item.
Returns:
true if a help item with the given label was found, otherwise, false.
